title: #92Noon! 9am Hour 6/29 - Florio/Pettine/Naima
description: –PA opens with seeking a truce with Florio, then Vikings Coach Mike Pettine joins to talk about his transition and working with the defense, and Naima from Cities joins to discuss London and hidden gems there.
